sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Endpoint
    participant Mediator
    participant Handler
    participant DB as Database
    participant Cache as Redis

    Client->>Endpoint: GET /api/v1/notifications?unreadOnly=true

    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Extract query params
    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Create GetNotificationsQuery

    Endpoint->>Mediator: Send(query)

    Mediator->>Handler: Handle(query)

    Handler->>Cache: TryGetCached("notifications:{userId}")
    Cache-->>Handler: Cache miss

    Handler->>DB: Query notifications
    Note over DB: WHERE UserId = userId<br/>AND IsRead = false<br/>ORDER BY CreatedAt DESC

    DB-->>Handler: List<Notification>

    Handler->>Handler: Map to NotificationDto[]

    Handler->>DB: Count unread
    DB-->>Handler: UnreadCount = 8

    Handler->>Cache: SetCached("notifications:{userId}", result, TTL: 30s)
    Cache-->>Handler: Cached ✓

    Handler-->>Mediator: PaginatedNotificationResult
    Mediator-->>Endpoint: PaginatedNotificationResult

    Endpoint-->>Client: 200 OK
    Note left of Client: {notifications[], unreadCount: 8}
